VALUES ('Chinese Landscape Painting Pigment Squeeze', 'A highly creative prompt that instructs the AI to generate an image based on a Ming Dynasty painting style (Qiu Ying''s ''Fairyland of Peach Blossoms''). The goal is to visualize a giant tube of mineral pigment being squeezed out, forming a 3D landscape of mountains and clouds in the traditional ''Blue-and-Green'' style, complete with traditional Chinese art props.', '<instruction>
