also make watermark "doctorwasif" at bottom right corner', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G-Z11YwXwAABkjV.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/doctorwasif/status/2010423848018100258", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-11T18:49:31.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Doctor Wasif\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/doctorwasif\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
