The Selfie Architecture: On the laptop screen, she is holding a smartphone with a distinctive blue-and-white cloud-patterned case, capturing her own reflection.
Quality & Lighting:

Lighting: High-key, bright, and optimistic morning light. The contrast between the bright screen and the natural room light is perfectly balanced.
Quality: Raw smartphone photo aesthetic, high dynamic range, visible subtle moir√© patterns on the laptop screen pixels, 8k resolution. Single frame.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G-Ov6ZDXwAED9nw.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/daaaaanc/status/2009644963194105910", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-09T15:14:31.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Dan Reed\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/daaaaanc\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
