VALUES ('Moody Fashion Editorial Rainy Night Prompt', 'A highly specific prompt for a moody, high-contrast fashion editorial snapshot taken on a rainy night, emphasizing raw, unedited realism and hard smartphone flash. It includes detailed instructions for bio-fidelity (skin physics, vellus hair), clothing tension (leather jacket and micro-mini skirt), and environment details (sharp focus on raindrops and cherry blossoms).', '(Vertical 9:16 smartphone aspect ratio). A raw, high-contrast [Moody Fashion Editorial] snapshot taken with an iPhone 17 Pro on a rainy night. DIRECT HARD SMARTPHONE FLASH. NO ARTIFICIAL BOKEH. Everything is SHARP and in focus from the frozen raindrops to the distant blossoms.

