INSERT INTO cinematic_prompts (title, description, prompt_text, category, tags, image_urls, metadata)
VALUES ('Photorealistic Candid Street Portrait with Extreme Shallow DOF', 'A highly detailed prompt for generating a photorealistic, candid street-fashion portrait. The core intent is to achieve extreme shallow depth of field, keeping a single subject tack-sharp in the mid-ground while rendering a moving crowd and the city background as soft blur/bokeh. It specifies composition, lighting (cinematic soft contrast), and critical camera optics (telephoto lens, wide aperture).', 'Core Intent: Create a photorealistic candid street-fashion portrait with extreme shallow depth of field where a single woman is sharply in focus in the mid-ground, surrounded by a moving crowd rendered as soft blur/bokeh. Preserve the exact framing, subject placement, color grade, and atmosphere.

1) Composition & Framing (LOCK)

‚Ä¢Aspect: 4:5 vertical.

‚Ä¢Camera height: chest-to-eye level (slightly above the subject‚Äôs shoulder line).

‚Ä¢Framing: mid-ground subject centered slightly left-of-center, from upper chest to top of head clearly visible; shoulders included; background heavily blurred.

‚Ä¢Foreground: two large blurred human shapes frame the subject:

‚Ä¢Left foreground: blurred middle-aged man occupying left third, grey/blue jacket, face out of focus.

‚Ä¢Right foreground: blurred person occupying right-lower quadrant (dark hair), also out of focus.

‚Ä¢Mid-right: blurred older bald man head/shoulder visible behind subject‚Äôs right shoulder.

‚Ä¢Background: dense city street with yellow taxi/cab shapes and warm orange bokeh lights; tall urban forms dissolve into creamy blur.

2) Subject (Primary)

‚Ä¢Person: young adult woman, fair/light skin, subtle freckles, natural editorial beauty.

‚Ä¢Hair: medium brown, messy low updo/bun with loose wisps; slightly damp/urban texture; flyaways framing face.

‚Ä¢Expression: calm, slightly serious/curious; lips relaxed; eyes looking directly toward camera with a soft, neutral intensity.

‚Ä¢Pose: body facing right (3/4 profile), head turned back over left shoulder to look at camera.

3) Wardrobe & Accessories (Exact Feel)

‚Ä¢Outerwear: {argument name="outerwear color" default="beige/tan"} trench coat (matte cotton), collar open, classic lapels, slightly rumpled city-wear texture.

‚Ä¢Bag: small shoulder bag with thin gold chain strap on her right shoulder; strap catches a bit of light; bag itself mostly hidden.

‚Ä¢Jewelry: small earring visible (subtle, warm tone).

4) Environment (Street Mood)

‚Ä¢Busy metropolitan sidewalk/street scene, crowd density high.

‚Ä¢Background palette: teal/green-grey city haze + yellow cab + warm orange bokeh lights.

‚Ä¢No readable signage, no sharp background details‚Äîeverything behind subject remains creamy blur.

5) Lighting (LOCK)

‚Ä¢Natural daylight, overcast-to-soft sun (diffused), no harsh shadows.

‚Ä¢Subject face evenly lit with gentle highlights on cheekbones and nose; cinematic soft contrast.

6) Camera & Optics (CRITICAL)

‚Ä¢Look: telephoto candid portrait with strong compression.

‚Ä¢Lens: 85mm‚Äì135mm range, wide open (f/1.4‚Äìf/2.0).

‚Ä¢Focus: tack-sharp on subject‚Äôs eyes and eyelashes; foreground and background strongly out of focus.

‚Ä¢Depth: creamy bokeh, smooth falloff, mild cat-eye bokeh at edges.

‚Ä¢Shutter/feel: background crowd appears naturally blurred from DOF; slight motion blur suggested in foreground figures.

7) Color Science / Grade (LOCK)

‚Ä¢Cinematic teal/green wash in shadows and background.

‚Ä¢Warm highlights (skin tones natural, slightly warm).

‚Ä¢Yellow taxi pops softly; orange bokeh lights glow.

‚Ä¢Fine', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G-CV_FEa0AAmStF.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/SimplyAnnisa/status/2008770349715030096", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-07T05:19:07.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Anissa\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/SimplyAnnisa\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
