VALUES ('Raw High-Definition Printed Portrait Aesthetic Prompt', 'A highly detailed prompt designed to emulate a raw, high-definition photograph of a physical printed portrait, capturing the texture of the paper and ink. It focuses heavily on realism, specific lighting (harsh studio flash), and includes a creative text overlay, ideal for generating yearbook or vintage magazine archive aesthetics.', '(3:4). A raw, high-definition photograph of a physical printed portrait taken with an iPhone 17 Pro. NO ARTIFICIAL BOKEH. Everything is SHARP and in focus, capturing the physical textural reality of the paper grain and the ink-on-page in high resolution.

