INSERT INTO cinematic_prompts (title, description, prompt_text, category, tags, image_urls, metadata)
VALUES ('Low-Resolution Motion-Blurred Selfie with Cat', 'A highly specific negative prompt designed to generate a raw, imperfect, low-resolution smartphone selfie aesthetic, featuring a woman and a cat with natural, uneven motion blur caused by poor camera quality and movement, explicitly forbidding high-quality features like sharp focus or AI enhancement.', 'Use the uploaded reference photo. Low-resolution smartphone close-up selfie taken with a broken front camera screen. The image shows strong natural motion blur concentrated on the woman‚Äôs face, hair, and the cat, caused by weak autofocus, slow shutter speed, and slight hand movement while lying down. Blur appears uneven and organic, with soft smearing rather than smooth artificial blur. Facial features are partially obscured but still recognizable, with eyes, nose, and mouth visible as softened shapes. A young woman lies intimately on a cream-colored leather sofa. A light brown cat with bright green eyes is lying on the woman‚Äôs chest, pressing its body close and nuzzling its face against the woman‚Äôs cheek and jaw, partially covering her face. The cat‚Äôs head and the woman‚Äôs face overlap closely, creating intimate contact. Both the woman‚Äôs face and the cat‚Äôs face are noticeably blurred together, with softened edges and slight motion smear from small movements and breathing. The woman‚Äôs long brown hair is loose and slightly messy, falling over her forehead and partially blending into the cat‚Äôs fur due to blur. Hair strands appear heavily softened but still natural, not melted or warped. The cat‚Äôs fur texture is mostly lost, appearing as soft blurred patches consistent with low resolution and motion. Overall sharpness is low, with inconsistent focus across the frame ‚Äî some tiny areas accidentally a bit clearer while most of the face and the cat remain out of focus. Flat, noisy skin texture with visible ISO noise, chroma noise, mild color banding, and muddy shadows typical of a cheap phone camera. The woman looks toward the lens with a soft, relaxed, intimate expression, though details are softened by blur. She wears simple, light-colored casual clothing, with fabric texture mostly lost. Lighting comes only from indoor room lights at night, slightly too bright, with mild overexposed highlights that do not completely blow out facial structure. Perspective distortion from the front camera wide-angle lens creates subtle stretching near the edges. The composition is very tight, awkward, and unintentional, filling the frame with the woman‚Äôs face and the cat‚Äôs body and head. The image feels like a raw, accidental selfie straight from the phone gallery ‚Äî imperfect, intimate, noisy, naturally blurred, completely unedited, with no beautification and no AI enhancement.  NEGATIVE WARNINGS (important): high resolution, sharp focus, DSLR, cinematic lighting, studio lighting, ultra-detail, clean skin texture, beauty filter, HDR, professional photo, sharp edges, smooth look, AI enhancement, overprocessing, perfect blur, depth-of-field bokeh. ar 9:16', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G994WU9bcAIDDAK.jpg","https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G994WYYaMAA5pJa.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/SimplyAnnisa/status/2008456291505893474", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-06T08:31:09.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Anissa\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/SimplyAnnisa\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
